Over their last four games, Everton (12), Chelsea (12) & Wolves (13) led the way for big chances, behind only Man City (15) & Liverpool (16h (who played 5 games in the same period). #FPL

Chelsea over the past eight gameweeks have conceded the fewest (41) shots in the box, less than half the volume of those conceded by Aston Villa (87) in the same period. #FPL

Ayoze Perez (£6.2m) is behind only Mo Salah (£12.8m) in terms of points for all midfields over the past eight gameweeks (47 compared to Salah’s 61). KDB (£10.8m, 45) Jordan Henderson (£5.5m, 44), Jack Grealish (£6.7m, 43) & Riyad Mahrez (£8.6m, 43) complete the top six. #FPL

Arsenal (55) & Crystal Palace (57) collectively attempted 112 assists over the past eight gameweeks, eight less than Man City (118). #FPL

Liverpool players collectively amassed a colossal 558 points over the past eight gameweeks - a massive 169 ahead of Watford, who are in second with 389. Everton are third with 372. Bournemouth prop up the table having accrued just 210 in that period. (38% of LFC’s total). #FPL
